  "text": "We observed an increased risk for both invasive and borderline EOCs (nonsignificant association in borderline) with a high intake of trans fat. [CITATION_1] also reported a positive association between trans fat intake and risk of invasive EOC, while the pooled analysis [CITATION_2] observed no association. Further data are needed to evaluate the association between trans fat intake and risk of invasive and borderline EOC.",
